After 2 years of work on this album and long waiting we get this intelligent pack of music, Contrast records proudly to release moshics 3rd album ?Hiloola?, after his astonishing Masterpiece 2nd album ?Salamat? who influenced the progressive house and down tempo world music fans with moshics amazing combination of ethnic, atmospheric and futuristic sound and style.

?Hiloola? is a double studio album, include a progressive house CD and a down tempo CD that continue to exhibit his individual sound and style, the one who made him well known among millions of fans around the globe.
